extends ../layout 

block content 
  .container 
    h1.text-center.mt-5 평가 리스트

    if(projects[0])
      each project in projects
        .card-group
          .card
            .card-body
              h3.card-title.mb-3.d-flex.justify-content-center= project.project_name
              .d-grid.gap-2.mt-2
                a.btn.btn-outline-dark(href=`/eval/evaluate/${project.project_no}`) 평가하기
    else 
      .card-group
        .card.text-center.p-5
          h5 평가 가능한 프로젝트가 없습니다.